[Command("toggleprefix")]
[Alias(new string[]{"togglenoprefix"})]
[Parameters("[channel id]")]
[Remarks("Put a channel in \"No Prefix mode\"")]
[Summary("When used by a user with the Manage Channels permission, toggles a channel between **Normal** mode and **No Prefix** mode.\nIn No Prefix mode, all commands will work without the need to use a prefix such as \"<\".\nIf the channel id is not specified, you will beasked to confirm the change for the current channel.\n\n**Warning!** This can result in a lot of unnecessary spam. Only use this if you're sure. It's a good idea only in dedicated channels, for example named \"#pacman\" or \"#botspam\"")]
